{"tid":1108181,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 你認為東南亞係咪南亞嘅一部分？","createTime":"2019-04-15T18:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T09:46:01.000Z","uid":49136,"like":68,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0629270517fc1fb83682846c8a4c8bd79b235170","tid":1108181,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T18:56:37.000Z","msg":"今次公投係因為最近連登好多人將東南亞國家，例如：大馬、泰國、印尼等地視為南亞國家，加上hk01都將馬六甲海峽一帶定為南亞國家，所以我希望透過公投了解連登人嘅睇法<br />\n<br />\nHK01記者：印尼係南亞國家！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1108135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1108135</a><br />\n<br />\n正評=東南亞就係東南亞<br />\n負評=東南亞屬於南亞/求撚其<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rt1K41A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRt1K41A.png&h=538b7584&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOZAseX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOZAseX.png&h=743f3c68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8f869ed74101856fa718fc36ab3b5e4b5975b99","tid":1108181,"uid":92376,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T19:02:32.000Z","msg":"有啲嘢必須分清楚 唔應該是是旦當係同一樣嘢<br />\n就好似玫瑰崗指蠙為蝻事件咁<br />\n連登仔將一個屬於東南亞地區既劣質民族講成蝻<br />\n變相無異於係放生咗蠙蠙<br />\n佢地唔會覺得比人鬧緊<br />\n因為屌既係南亞<br />\n印度 巴基斯坦果一帶區域<br />\n蠙：無人屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以 真係唔需要分？<br />\n自己諗清楚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4abd598ade297e49ac56575f6c7a0414ad0730","tid":1108181,"uid":49136,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T19:05:04.000Z","msg":"本次公投限期係2019年4月30日<br />\n應該夠時間討論<br />\n多謝支持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d0bb